OL,3,CWales' 'strictest headteacher' on
OL,4,Cweekend detentions and parents in class
OL,6,FMr Alun Ebenezer has become known as
OL,7,FWales' strictest headteacher.
OL,9,FIntroducing Saturday detentions and
OL,10,Fpunishing pupils by demanding their
OL,11,Fparents come into school and sit with
OL,12,Fthem in class.
OL,14,FOriginally from Ebbw Vale, he was
OL,15,Fdrafted into Caldicot High School by
OL,16,FMonmouthshire Council ten months ago
OL,17,Fas an emergency measure.
