OL,3,CWales' 'strictest headteacher' on
OL,4,Cweekend detentions and parents in class
OL,6,FHe said, "Believe me, Saturday
OL,7,Fdetention is a huge hassle for me and
OL,8,FI don't want to be here on a Saturday
OL,9,Feither, but there needs to be
OL,10,Fconsequences for poor behaviour."
OL,12,FAt the start of his time in post, some
OL,13,Fparents complained about him sending
OL,14,Fgirls home for the length of their
OL,15,Fskirts. Mr Ebenezer denies claims that
OL,16,Fhe had been measuring skirts with a
OL,17,Ftape measure.
