OL,3,CWales' 'strictest headteacher' on
OL,4,Cweekend detentions and parents in class
OL,6,FHe said, "Throughout my career, I've
OL,7,Fhit the headlines over uniform,
OL,8,Fhairstyles, all sorts. And some of
OL,9,Fthat coverage has polarised opinion.
OL,11,F"I've been in the press a lot over the
OL,12,Flast year, and the reaction, in the
OL,13,Fmain, has been positive. That tells me
OL,14,Fthis has captured the mood of the
OL,15,Fnation.
OL,17,F"It's important because it all makes
OL,18,Ffor a brilliant culture. Uniform is
OL,19,Fabout pride and being proud of your
OL,20,Fschool and your community."
