OL,3,CWales' 'strictest headteacher' on
OL,4,Cweekend detentions and parents in class
OL,6,FOne big problem Mr Ebenezer explains
OL,7,Fis the use of social media, making
OL,8,Fyoung people to focus on themselves
OL,9,Ftoo much.
OL,11,FHe said, "We've told young people to
OL,12,Ffocus on themselves, but it's making
OL,13,Fthem miserable. We live in a day and
OL,14,Fage now where we tell young people,
OL,15,F'Be whatever you want to be that makes
OL,16,Fyou happy.'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
