OL,3,CWales' 'strictest headteacher' on
OL,4,Cweekend detentions and parents in class
OL,6,F"And 'The most important thing is that
OL,7,Fyou're happy.' We've rammed this down
OL,8,Ftheir throats, this obsession with
OL,9,Fbeing really happy, and yet they've
OL,10,Fnever been more entertained, but
OL,11,Fthey're bored, and they've never been
OL,12,Fmore indulged, but they're unhappy.
OL,14,F"It's not working. Equally I don't
OL,15,Fbelieve in beating this generation up
OL,16,Ffor that. We created this generation."
