OL,3,CWales' 'strictest headteacher' on
OL,4,Cweekend detentions and parents in class
OL,6,FLooking to the future, he has worked
OL,7,Fwith his assistant head to put
OL,8,Ftogether a co-curriculum for next
OL,9,Fyear, which he hopes will be among the
OL,10,Fbest in the nation.
OL,12,FIt'll include trips to Africa and
OL,13,FSouth America and is all part of
OL,14,Fchanging a culture in the hope that
OL,15,Fwhen he leaves, Caldicot High will be
OL,16,Fin the top 20 best comps in Wales.
